Description: Yet another bar for Linux on Wayland session
 HuskyPanel is a shell bar panel for Linux Wayland sessions, built with Qt 6
 and QML to deliver a Material Design 3 styled UI. Currently targeting KDE
 Plasma 6 / KWin.
